`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Cure_Disease
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'cure disease' <target>

 This spell is used to cure the symptoms of plague in the target.  If no target
is given, the spell will automatically be cast upon the person casting the
spell.

